title: Australia 30 Year bond-Yield
description: Australia 30 Year Bond Yield was 4.12 percent on Friday November 11, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Australia 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 4.62 in October of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for Australia 30Y.
